description: Learn how to insult a person like a boss using the Unofficial Trump Insult Generator.  This Alexa app pulls together several random one sentence Donald Trump's quotes and strings them together with a first name to insult a person.  What insult will you generate?
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask insult generator to generate insult for Jessica
name: Unofficial Trump Insult Generator
shortDescription: The Unofficial Trump Insult Generator pulls together some of Donald Trump's random quotes and strings them together with a first name to insult a person.
